# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo
# On checkout, convert to native line endings (CRLF on Windows)
* text=auto

# Markdown: always LF (Obsidian saves LF even on Windows)
# Without this, text=auto converts to CRLF on checkout,
# then Obsidian overwrites with LF, creating false git diffs
*.md text eol=lf

